description.narrative: Capacity of national and state level education functionaries enhanced in designing and implementation of robust and responsive large-scale and school-based assessments; for demonstration and scale up of child- centered teaching learning practices ; and local learning hubs such as block and cluster resource centres equipped to provide on-site supportive supervision and academic leadership to deliver equitable quality education and improving learning outcomes of children. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:13/01/2020
